Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that you've remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the freak beast's intelligence is at the level of a beast too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'll make you remember soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so he is that brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...who killed his entire clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Kakashi, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Sharingan... Just like Sasuke's!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is the... one who's tormenting Sasuke and Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just me, but Gaara too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will destroy you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Don't look directly\Nat his eyes! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:30.35,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\bord4\blur4\fax0.18\fad(651,643)\pos(700,570)}A Meeting With Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suiton: Bakusui Shouha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Suiton: Bakusui Shouha - Water Style: Exploding Water Shock Wave)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi's Genjutsu is a Visual Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's a type where\None gets caught by his sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so it'll be okay as long as we don't make eye contact with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But then... How should we fight him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gai, how did you fight with Itachi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Decipher his actions just by how he moves his body and feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha clan, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since\NI went up against a Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be that surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a few fighting techniques to counter his Visual Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"If it's one against one, then you must flee."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"If it's two against one, the take the back."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what "if it's one against one, then you must flee" means right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's two against one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's two against one, even if one is caught by the Genjutsu, the other will take his back and hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Genjutsu will cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if you hit your teammate,\Nthen you can end the Genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if there is more than one of us,\Nthen one will distract him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of us will constantly attack him from the back where the Sharingan can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, you know a lot from old age!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll take his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Neji! Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So... how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it remind you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he let out this much water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This technique requires a huge amount of Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a technique like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi-sensei, what do you mean by wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say my way of fighting the Sharingan is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That would work if it's an ordinary Genjutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's a bit more complicated in his case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He uses Mangekyo Sharingan which is a much stronger Visual Technique than an ordinary Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you receive his Visual Technique, then you will experience his Genjutsu in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, even though it may seem like a second to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who receives the technique will feel it for hours or days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case, I roamed around in his technique for three days, and lost consciousness for more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of ending or not ending the Genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who exactly is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you didn't suffer my Tsukiyomi in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not all that I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After you used the Visual Technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you were quite exhausted and you ended the battle immediately and tried to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Itachi... Even for you, it is dangerous to use that "eye" too much...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We did not come here to fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unfortunately, anything more than this is nonsense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to using up quite a lot of Chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems it comes with some risk to your "eye" as well, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From just one match, you have analyzed it quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You eyesight... How much has it weakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi... Could it be that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai-sensei! Tenten!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A Water Clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even have time to recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems like Itachi also has come into contact with the enemy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kisame is in the middle of a fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konoha Shoufuu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Konoha Shoufuu: Leaf Rising Wind)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hakke Kuushou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Hakke Kuushou: 8 Trigrams, Air Palm)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's programmed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Neji, where's the enemy location?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In front! He's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously... What troublesome brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Water Style Ninjutsu and that big sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you have finally remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I do feel like we have met somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You still can't remember, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}are{\i0} good at hurting people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you recall... I will take my time putting you through pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated you back then.\NBut I'm not that pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to work the way it did before, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge mistake if you think\NI'm the same as before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, I'll deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This happened before too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Form the Manji. You guys look after Tazuna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't get involved in the fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And work as a team here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You mean another non-fighting teamwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This time, cover me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I want to be cool and say, "Go on ahead", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Against him, even I can't contain him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll get him off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I succeed, don't hesitate to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll get me off guard that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will quickly change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Juuken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Juuken: Gentle Fist)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You swing that heavy sword so easily and you don't get caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If close battle does not work...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What an annoying sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your weapon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell by looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a big difference between knowing it and {\i1}really{\i0} knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, Gai-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Each word holds a deep meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now for god's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you quit being amazed every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Tenten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take back what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like your intelligence\Nis less than an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynamic Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time for you to come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Clone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rasengan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is also a Shadow Clone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura! Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mizu Bunshin no Jutsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Mizu Bunshin no Jutsu: Water Clone Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suirou no Jutsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Suirou no Jutsu: Water Prison Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee! Neji! Tenten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
